  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "For more than a decade, Kor'sarro Khan of the White Scars has pursued a single quarry across the stars: Kernax Voldorius, a daemon prince and warleader of the treacherous Alpha Legion. The hunt finally runs its prey to ground on Quintus, a world wholly corrupted and given over to the renegades' cause. To bring down so monstrous a foe, the swift riders of the White Scars must forge an unlikely alliance with the shadow-warriors of the Raven Guard and their captain, Kayvaan Shrike. Together they face an entire planet in arms, knowing that a hunt this long can end only in the daemon's death or their own. A relentless story of vengeance, honour and the price of an unbreakable oath.",
